899
01:12:57,688 --> 01:12:58,842
<i>Park Dong Hoon.</i>

900
01:12:58,842 --> 01:13:00,976
Saat dia mengetahui kaulah
kandidat paling mumpuni...

901
01:13:00,976 --> 01:13:02,602
...kau harus waspada.

902
01:13:02,602 --> 01:13:06,397
Jika kau tidak menyerang,
kau akan benar-benar hancur.

903
01:13:06,397 --> 01:13:09,322
Pastikan hancurkan
bajingan Do Joon Young itu.

904
01:13:09,322 --> 01:13:11,568
<i>Tunjukkan padanya apa keadilan itu!</i>

905
01:13:12,383 --> 01:13:13,557
